reviewText: Helped preschooler fall asleep. Vivid and engaging yet not over stimulating. This was a rental but am considering purchase after viewing other volumes that weren't as good.
By far our most favorite of all the series! The scenery is perfectly paired to the music. We never tire of watching this video and calms even the most over-tired viewer!

My 16 month old twins love this and sleep contently thru the night with it playing.  They will wake up in the morning and peacefully watch it until I go into their room.  You can't go wrong with this purchase.  I have spread the word that this works.
